Package: reptiledb.data
Title: Reptile Database Data
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Paul Efren",
        family = "Santos Andrade",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "paulefrens@gmail.com",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6635-0375")
    ))
Description: Provides easy access to 'The Reptile Database', a comprehensive 
    catalogue of all living reptile species and their classification. This 
    package contains taxonomic data for over 10,000 reptile species including 
    approximately 2,800 subspecies, covering all living snakes, lizards, 
    turtles, amphisbaenians, tuataras, and crocodiles. The dataset includes 
    taxonomic names and synonyms, distribution data, type specimens, and 
    literature references, making it ready for herpetological research and 
    analysis. Data is sourced from 'The Reptile Database' 
    <http://www.reptile-database.org/>.
